pl.bristleback.server.bristle.api.annotations

Annotation Type ObjectSender


  • @Target(value={TYPE,FIELD})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ObjectSender
    All ConditionObjectSender fields must be marked with this annotation to be properly initialized by Bristleback Server. All non default serialization operations are defined within this annotation.
